body_html: Unfortunately we have not built or tested on Mac OS sierra yet. I will keep this open and let you know. We're not sure if it is a underlying Bazel not supporting MacOS sierra or if it is a tensorflow. @gunan, @jart any thoughts? Another issue is having Sierra issues too (http://github.com/tensorflow/models/issues/599).
